# Cursor Rule — Database and Prisma

Use PostgreSQL through Prisma.
Do not use MongoDB.
Separate Voucher from VoucherCode.
Use enums for statuses.
Use unique index for voucher code.
Use transaction/atomic updates for checkout and redeem.
Do not update voucher quantity outside checkout transaction.
